Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:14.70,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,320)\fad(600,0)}不\N倒\N翁\N跌\N倒\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第4話出現的類似一二三木頭人的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班會已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫助老奶奶了這個理由上次已經使用過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽不在家也成不了理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊  我要怎麼辯解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少給我過哪怕一輛車啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我碰到了四次紅燈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果連第一節課都開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:17.49,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N40
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個顯而易見的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會被這麼經典的陷阱砸中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  雙重夾擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？  這對我做出的遲到制裁算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底犯下了什麼過錯啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  從後門偷偷地溜進去就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  沒必要故意從正面進去惹老師生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！  從下面的門溜進去就沒問題了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像空氣般悄悄潛入  自然地上課就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道了啦  做這種事的除了「老大」就沒有別人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  從下面溜進去  被發現的話感覺更會惹老師生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要被發現  我就乾脆從上面的窗子進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在窗戶上鑲嵌了彩繪玻璃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下等下  我為什麼要跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從教室逃走什麼也解決不了問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  從哪裡進去是最佳方案這才是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然無論我怎麼做最終老師都會生氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就堂堂正正地從正面突破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來個寧為玉碎不為瓦全還比較有型啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  最佳方案是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面的這個黑板刷！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊吃一記黑板刷  一邊笑容滿面地入場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後用同學們綻開的笑臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回到座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要開朗地  精神飽滿地當一個小丑哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出場！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就等不及說句早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一節課在LL教室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:02.41,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,280)\fad(600,600)}肥\N皂\N泡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大工麵包，大工是日常裡設定的當地的財團。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無敵星人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼蠢事啊  又不是小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無敵星人對於一切攻擊都是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.69,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,330)\fs30\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}B\Nl\Nu\Ne\N\Nn\No\Nt\Ne
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:52.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美國爵士樂唱片公司，也可以指某種爵士樂音階。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裡指Miles Davis（1926-1991），美國黑人傳奇爵士小號樂手\N上世紀50年代曾在Blue note錄製過經典爵士大碟。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miles他會自殺的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  一不小心就入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到我吹了嗎  阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽也好其他也好  這是什麼拷問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵都要壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再吹一遍  你好好聽著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽人說話啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}流水拉麵活動在時定公園舉辦  白天舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像附近的公園在舉辦流水拉麵活動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為流水拉麵我只在電視上看過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天我超級期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不在前面等著就夾不到拉麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天什麼都沒有吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要佔據前排大吃特吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:12.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}流水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:17.35,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N41
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次碰到你這樣的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…不好意思  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊！  一口都沒吃到就要放棄嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的做法就算法律允許
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不允許哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你這樣說  但是我沒有筷子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要厚臉皮到什麼地步啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  馬上再來新的一輪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙筷子被人使用過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是環保
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間可是不等人的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  就用另一頭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一下下的小幽默啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就要來真的了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你見識到真正的地獄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為每次都有流水然後就安逸地站在那裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能瞻前不顧後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你裝什麼大和撫子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要稍微去體會食材的美味啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那裡猶豫不決了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣前怎能畏畏縮縮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是完全沒改變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:23.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}江木正晴，流水拉麵研究家。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正晴啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一聽到公園在舉辦流水拉麵的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就猜到是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我認為正晴一定會出現  就舉辦了流水拉麵活動…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了追求究極的流水拉麵  你踏上旅程的30年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了所有的流水拉麵之後  我開始變得迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我們的存款帶走而踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那些錢都用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸根結底是流水拉麵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至少放點水把
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看什麼看啊  這可不是表演啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  你能不能像流水拉麵一樣趕快離開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句話時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級生都集合完畢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好  有順境成才的人  也有逆境成才的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都由老師來判斷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是順境成才  卻完全沒有被表揚過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:08.06,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,290)\fad(400,600)}N\NA\NS\NA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我這麼說了就發射吧  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著把頭髮綁起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  稍稍有點姐姐的感覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:50.23,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N42
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  博士有多像姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  非常像姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼名乃呢  名乃有多像？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我恐怕沒有那麼像姐姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得妙  是的  恐怕是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  既然沒辦法  就讓博士來收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾呀收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  名乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我還在看這本書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  阪本也讓人操心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然這樣  你有什麼陰謀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本你真是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會啦  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你要幫我蓋的話就用毛巾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要用書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  阪本  你這是強詞奪理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗衣服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士我來洗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係哦  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只要把計時器轉一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就由博士來轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  真的只要轉一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了博士我要轉啦  讓博士來轉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有困難請找博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿名乃沒辦法  就由博士來做飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  我現在已經在做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士做的更好吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…你看  住手啦  很危險的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}博士我會做的  沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓我來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可看不出有什麼沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  燙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙死了  燙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你…你沒事吧  阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都做了什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿阪本你沒辦法啊  在這種地方走來走去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法你個頭啦  還不都是你們瞎搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  阪本  生氣也解決不了什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你在講什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之再重新煎個蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那麼就由博士來煎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  其他的菜會冷掉的  所以要快點煎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  名乃啊  博士都說了我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  博士  很危險的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋會掉下去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小姑娘  今天這個小鬼是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想做姐姐感覺的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是姐姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐可是不吃零食的  你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘  變回平時的博士啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我蒙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.98,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,300)\fad(600,0)}河\N邊\N垂\N釣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看來是條大魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是長筒靴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這次才是真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是水壺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上這不是比魚還要厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會有這麼有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該邀請別人一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:48.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}桃太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒手壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.58,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N43
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底為什麼我非得做作業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  雖然說我確實成績不好  不做不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是具備設法回避不及格的能力的  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升學沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不想畢業了再到大學去繼續讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就業？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是之前在電視上看到就業難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有學歷的話很難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就職
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法避免的大學入學考試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是不想學習！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底現在進行的學習對將來有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來的夢想是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來的夢想  相生祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將來的夢想是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成傘蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘蜥  傘蜥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想學習！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想學習也不想變成傘蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來說要是變成傘蜥蜴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會擺脫這個煩惱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果反正要變的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆變成國寶大師受到追捧也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:56.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}粘土般的某物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說國寶大師每月能賺多少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要怎樣才能變成國寶大師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸根結底  國寶大師是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  還是更加現實地考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為的東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為的東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為的東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了啊  完全找不到方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我才高一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有整整三年的考慮時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣都無法得出結論的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學考試！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不想學習！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  就算氣餒也沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為考慮我想成為的東西才苦惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就應該試著先去考慮自己想做什麼不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:08.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}體！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砰砰砰的吵死了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點了啊！
