Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:28.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}24小時滿腦子都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:29.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}意識不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:32.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}覺得與平時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:31.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}覺\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:34.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}兩\N個\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:38.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}難道  不對  是單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:36.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}兩\N情\N相\N悅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:40.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟了  視線和他對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:44.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什麼什麼  這種忐忑心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:50.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思考回路亂成一團
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:56.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那種事情  我可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:00.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感覺都要發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:04.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急轉直下的我的愛慕之情
